dataList.content: It's a freight container, made of smooth plastic that comes in assorted colors.
The use of so many peculiar materials suggests that this is more than just a basic manufacturing facility.
Almost on cue, the eerily colorful container facility whirred to life, chirping a cheerful tune.
I've got a bad feeling about this...
Why aren't there any guards on this floor?
The answer revealed itself before anyone could voice their uncertainty.
The containers finished cycling and their doors slid open. Out came...
